room_title: Escape room "The Recruits" by Bangor Escape Rooms in Bangor
room_description: You're a group of CIA trainees that are put in this room as your final test. In the CIA, nothing is what it seems. Upon entering, a fail safe was initiated that will lead to a missile launch in exactly 60 minutes. Your objective is to find the code that will stop the launch to prevent civilian casualty. Do you have what it takes to pass your final test?
